cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM 

This paper deals with the task of generating human images, which is a common problem in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed solution is based on attention mechanisms, which are a popular technique in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the use of multiple source images, which could be considered a problem in graphics (cs.GR) or multimedia (cs.MM).
